## Key Constraints

- Single user, local deployment — no auth, no DB, no multi-tenancy
- Runs fully offline after data ingestion
- 10K Monte Carlo sims must complete in <30 seconds
- All math must be traceable to peer-reviewed research or validated public rating systems
- Weight dicts are external JSON configs — never hardcode weights
